<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='218:245'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-1a' );" name="013-1a" class="pb">[013-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='245:253'>儀禮卷第十三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='253:268'>旣夕禮第十三　儀禮　鄭氏注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='268:301'>旣夕哭<span class='krp-note'>旣巳也謂岀門/哭止復外位時</span>請啓期告于賔<span class='krp-note'>將葬/當遷</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='301:338'><span class='krp-note'>柩于祖有司於是乃請啓肂之期於主/人以告賔賔冝知其時也今文啓爲開</span>夙興</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='338:365'>設盥于祖廟門外<span class='krp-note'>祖王父也下/士祖禰共廟</span>陳鼎皆如殯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='365:394'>東方之饌亦如之<span class='krp-note'>皆皆三鼎也如殯/如大歛旣殯之奠</span>夷牀饌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='394:425'>于階間<span class='krp-note'>夷之言尸也朝/正柩用此牀</span>二燭俟于殯門外<span class='krp-note'>早/關</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='425:456'><span class='krp-note'>以爲明也/燭用烝</span>丈夫髽散帶垂即位如初<span class='krp-note'>爲將啓/變也此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='456:483'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-1b' );" name="013-1b" class="pb">[013-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='483:522'><span class='krp-note'>互文以相見耳髽婦人之變䘮服小記曰男/子免而婦人髽男子冠而婦人笄如初朝夕</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='522:553'><span class='krp-note'>哭門/外位</span>婦人不哭主人拜賔入即位袒<span class='krp-note'>此不象/如𥘉者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='553:583'><span class='krp-note'>以男子入門不哭也不/哭者將有事止讙囂</span>商祝免袒執功布入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='583:607'>升自西階盡階不升堂聲三啓三命哭<span class='krp-note'>功布/灰治</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='607:646'><span class='krp-note'>之布也執之以接神爲有所拂㧍也聲三三/有聲存神也啓三三言啓告神也舊說以爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='646:678'><span class='krp-note'>聲噫興也今/文免作絻</span>燭入<span class='krp-note'>炤徹與/啓肂者</span>祝降與夏祝交于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='678:710'>階下取銘置于重<span class='krp-note'>祝降者祝徹宿奠降也與/夏祝交事相接也夏祝取</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='710:748'><span class='krp-note'>銘置于重爲啓肂遷之吉事交相/左凶事交相右今文銘皆作名</span>踊無筭<span class='krp-note'>主/人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='748:775'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-2a' );" name="013-2a" class="pb">[013-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='775:804'><span class='krp-note'>也</span>商祝拂柩用功布幠用夷衾<span class='krp-note'>拂去塵也幠/覆之爲其形</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='804:839'><span class='krp-note'>露</span>遷于祖用軸<span class='krp-note'>遷徙也徙於祖朝祖庿也檀/弓曰殷朝而殯於祖周朝而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='839:878'><span class='krp-note'>遂葬蓋象平生將出必辭尊者軸輁軸也軸/狀如轉轔刻兩頭爲軹輁狀如長牀穿桯前</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='878:912'><span class='krp-note'>後著金而關軸焉大夫諸侯以上/有四周謂之輴天子畫之以龍</span>重先奠從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='912:942'>燭從柩從燭從主人從<span class='krp-note'>行之序也主人從者/丈夫由右婦人由左</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='942:979'><span class='krp-note'>以服之親䟽爲先後各從其/昭穆男賔在前女賔在後</span>升自西階<span class='krp-note'>柩也/猶用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='979:1009'><span class='krp-note'>子道不/由阼也</span>奠俟于下東面北上<span class='krp-note'>俟正/柩也</span>主人從升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1009:1033'>婦人升東面衆人東即位<span class='krp-note'>東方/之位</span>正柩于兩楹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1033:1060'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-2b' );" name="013-2b" class="pb">[013-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1060:1088'>間用夷牀<span class='krp-note'>兩楹間象鄕戶牖/也是時柩北首</span>主人柩東西面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1088:1112'>置重如初<span class='krp-note'>如殯宮/時也</span>席升設于柩西奠設如初</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1112:1145'>巾之升降自西階<span class='krp-note'>席設于柩之西直柩之西/當西階也從奠設如𥘉東</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1145:1181'><span class='krp-note'>面也不統於柩神不西面也不設柩/東東非神位也巾之者爲禦當風塵</span>主人踊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1181:1200'>無筭降拜賔即位踊襲主婦及親者由足西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1200:1237'>面<span class='krp-note'>設奠時婦人皆室戶西南面奠畢乃得東/面親者西面堂上迫䟽者可以居房中</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1237:1269'>薦車直東榮北輈<span class='krp-note'>薦進也進車者象生時將/行陳駕也今時謂之魂車</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1269:1302'><span class='krp-note'>輈轅也車當采榮/東陳西上於中庭</span>質明滅燭<span class='krp-note'>質正/也</span>徹者升自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1302:1329'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-3a' );" name="013-3a" class="pb">[013-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1329:1358'>阼階降自西階<span class='krp-note'>徹者辟新奠不設序/西南巳再設爲䙝</span>乃奠如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1358:1388'>初升降自西階<span class='krp-note'>爲遷祖奠也奠升不由/阼階柩北首辟其足</span>主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1388:1411'>要節而踊<span class='krp-note'>節升/降</span>薦馬纓三就入門北面交轡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1411:1445'>圉人夾牽之<span class='krp-note'>駕車之馬毎車二疋纓今馬鞅/也就成也諸侯之臣飾纓以三</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1445:1484'><span class='krp-note'>色而三成此三色者蓋絛絲也其著之如罽/然天子之臣如其命數王之革路絛纓圉人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1484:1521'><span class='krp-note'>養馬者在左右曰夾旣奠乃薦馬者爲/其踐汚庿中也凡入門參分庭一在南</span>御者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1521:1548'>執策立于馬後哭成踊右還出<span class='krp-note'>主人於是乃/哭踊者薦車</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1548:1577'><span class='krp-note'>之禮成/於薦馬</span>賔岀主人送于門外有司請祖期<span class='krp-note'>亦/因</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1577:1604'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-3b' );" name="013-3b" class="pb">[013-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1604:1643'><span class='krp-note'>在外位請之當以告賔每事畢/輒出將行而飮酒曰祖祖始也</span>曰日側<span class='krp-note'>側昳/也謂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1643:1672'><span class='krp-note'>將過中/之時</span>主人入袒乃載踊無筭卒束襲<span class='krp-note'>袒爲/載變</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1672:1707'><span class='krp-note'>也乃舉柩郤下而載之束束棺於柩/車賔出遂匠納車于階間謂此車</span>降奠當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1707:1741'>前束<span class='krp-note'>下遷祖之奠也當前束猶當戶/腢也亦在柩車西束有前後也</span>商祝飾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1741:1767'>柩一池紐前䞓後緇齊三采無貝<span class='krp-note'>飾柩爲設/牆栁也巾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1767:1806'><span class='krp-note'>奠乃牆謂此也牆有布帷栁有布荒池者象/官室之承霤以竹爲之狀如小車笭衣以青</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1806:1845'><span class='krp-note'>布一池縣於栁前士不揄絞紐所以聮帷荒/前赤後黒因以爲飾左右面各有前後齊居</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1845:1883'><span class='krp-note'>栁之中央若今小車蓋上㽔矣以三采繒爲/之上朱中白下蒼著以絮元士以上有貝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1883:1910'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-4a' );" name="013-4a" class="pb">[013-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1910:1947'>設披<span class='krp-note'>披輅栁棺上貫結於戴人居旁牽之以/備傾虧䘮大記曰士戴前纁後緇二披</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1947:1987'><span class='krp-note'>用纁今文/披皆爲藩</span>屬引<span class='krp-note'>屬猶著也引所以引柩車在/軸輴曰紼古者人引柩春秋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1987:2021'><span class='krp-note'>傳曰坐引/而哭之三</span>陳明器於乗車之西<span class='krp-note'>明器藏器也/檀弓曰其曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2021:2060'><span class='krp-note'>明器神明之也言神明者異於生器竹不成/用瓦不成味木不成斵琴瑟張而不平竽笙</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2060:2098'><span class='krp-note'>備而不和有鍾磬而無筍虡/陳器於乗車之西則重北也</span>折橫覆之<span class='krp-note'>折猶/庪也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2098:2137'><span class='krp-note'>方鑿連木爲之蓋如牀而縮者三橫者五無/簀窆事畢加之壙上以承抗席橫陳之者爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2137:2173'><span class='krp-note'>苞筲以下䋫於其北/便也覆之見善面也</span>抗木橫三縮二<span class='krp-note'>抗禦也/所以禦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2173:2205'><span class='krp-note'>止土者其横與/縮各足掩壙</span>加抗席三<span class='krp-note'>席所以/禦塵</span>加茵用䟽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2205:2232'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-4b' );" name="013-4b" class="pb">[013-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2232:2261'>布緇翦有幅亦縮二橫三<span class='krp-note'>茵所以藉棺者翦/淺也幅縁之亦者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2261:2299'><span class='krp-note'>亦抗木也及其用之木三在上茵二在下/象天三合地二人藏其中焉今文翦作淺</span>器</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2299:2333'>西南上綪<span class='krp-note'>器目言之也陳明器以西行南端/爲上綪屈也不容則屈而反之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2333:2367'>茵<span class='krp-note'>茵在杭木上陳/器次而北也</span>苞二<span class='krp-note'>所以裹奠/羊豕之肉</span>筲三黍稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2367:2396'>麥<span class='krp-note'>筲畚種類也其容/蓋與簋同一觳也</span>罋三醯醢屑幂用䟽布</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2396:2433'><span class='krp-note'>罋瓦器其容亦蓋一觳屑薑桂之屑也内/則曰屑桂與薑幂覆也今文幂皆作密</span>甒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2433:2460'>二醴酒幂用功布<span class='krp-note'>甒亦瓦器也古/文甒皆作廡</span>皆木桁久</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2460:2494'>之<span class='krp-note'>桁所以庪苞筲罋甒也久當爲炙/灸謂以蓋案塞其口毎器異桁</span>用器弓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2494:2502'><span class='krp-note'>席所以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2502:2529'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-5a' );" name="013-5a" class="pb">[013-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2529:2552'>矢耒耜兩敦兩杅槃匜匜實于槃中南流<span class='krp-note'>此/皆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2552:2590'><span class='krp-note'>常用之噐也杅盛湯漿槃匜盥/噐也流匜口也今文杅爲桙</span>無祭器<span class='krp-note'>士禮/略也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2590:2625'><span class='krp-note'>大夫以上兼用/鬼器人噐也</span>有燕樂器可也<span class='krp-note'>與賔客燕飲/用樂之器也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2625:2655'>役器甲胄干笮<span class='krp-note'>此皆師役之器甲鎧/胄兠鍪干楯笮矢箙</span>燕器杖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2655:2691'>笠翣<span class='krp-note'>燕居安體之器也/笠竹<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2131' title='KR2131' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2131.png'/>蓋也翣扇</span>徹奠巾席俟于西方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2691:2724'>主人要節而踊<span class='krp-note'>巾席俟於西方祖奠將用焉/要節者來象升丈夫踊去象</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2724:2763'><span class='krp-note'>降婦人踊徹者由明器北西面旣徹由重南/東不設於序西南者非宿奠也宿奠必設者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2763:2802'><span class='krp-note'>爲神馮依/之久也</span>袒<span class='krp-note'>爲將/袒變</span>商祝御柩<span class='krp-note'>亦執功布居前/爲還柩車爲節</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2802:2829'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-5b' );" name="013-5b" class="pb">[013-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2829:2856'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-5b' );" name="013-5b" class="pb">[013-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2856:2894'><span class='krp-note'>也兩馬士制也春秋傳曰宋景曹卒魯季康/子使冉求賵之以馬曰其可以稱旌繁乎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2894:2913'>擯者出請入吿主人釋杖迎于廟門外不哭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2913:2940'>先入門右北面及衆主人袒<span class='krp-note'>尊君命也衆主/人自若西面</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2940:2965'>馬入設<span class='krp-note'>設于庭/在重南</span>賔奉幣由馬西當前輅北面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2965:3002'>致命<span class='krp-note'>賔使者幣玄纁也輅轅縛所以屬引由/馬西則亦當前輅之西於是北面致命</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3002:3034'><span class='krp-note'>得郷柩與奠柩車在階間少/前參分庭之北輅有前後</span>主人哭拜稽顙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3034:3063'>成踊賔奠幣于棧左服出<span class='krp-note'>棧謂柩車也凡士/車制無漆飾左服</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3063:3092'><span class='krp-note'>象授人授其右也服/車箱今文棧作輚</span>宰由主人之北舉幣以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3092:3119'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-6a' );" name="013-6a" class="pb">[013-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3119:3154'>東<span class='krp-note'>柩東主人位/以東藏之</span>士受馬以出<span class='krp-note'>此士謂胥徒之/長也有勇力者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3154:3181'><span class='krp-note'>受馬聘禮曰皮/馬相間可也</span>主人送于外門外拜襲入復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3181:3206'>位杖賔賵者將命<span class='krp-note'>賔卿大/夫士也</span>擯者出請入告出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3206:3231'>告須<span class='krp-note'>不迎告曰/孤某須</span>馬入設賔奉幣擯者先入賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3231:3262'>從致命如初<span class='krp-note'>𥘉公/使者</span>主人拜于位不踊<span class='krp-note'>柩車東/位也旣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3262:3287'><span class='krp-note'>啓之後與/在室同</span>賔奠幣如初舉幣受馬如初擯者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3287:3320'>出請<span class='krp-note'>賔出在外請之/爲其復有事</span>若奠<span class='krp-note'>賔致可/以奠也</span>入告出以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3320:3345'>賔入將命如初士受羊如受馬又請<span class='krp-note'>士亦謂/胥徒之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3345:3372'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-6b' );" name="013-6b" class="pb">[013-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3372:3405'><span class='krp-note'>長又/復也</span>若賻<span class='krp-note'>賻之言𥙷也助/也貨財曰賻</span>入告主人出門左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3405:3432'>西面賔東面將命<span class='krp-note'>主人出者賻/主施於主人</span>主人拜賔坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3432:3457'>委之宰由主人之北東面舉之反位<span class='krp-note'>坐委之/明主人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3457:3490'><span class='krp-note'>哀戚志不在受人物反/位反主人之後位</span>若無器則捂受之<span class='krp-note'>謂/對</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3490:3518'><span class='krp-note'>相授不/委地</span>又請賔告事畢拜送入贈者將命<span class='krp-note'>贈/送</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3518:3543'>擯者出請納賔如初<span class='krp-note'>如其入告/出告須</span>賔奠幣如初</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3543:3576'><span class='krp-note'>亦於棧/左服</span>若就器則坐奠于陳<span class='krp-note'>就猶善也贈無/常唯玩好所有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3576:3608'><span class='krp-note'>陳明噐/之陳</span>凡將禮必請而後拜送<span class='krp-note'>雖知事畢猶/請君子不必</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3608:3635'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-7a' );" name="013-7a" class="pb">[013-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3635:3671'><span class='krp-note'>人/意</span>兄弟賵奠可也<span class='krp-note'>兄弟有服親者可且賵且/奠許其厚也賵奠於死生</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3671:3706'><span class='krp-note'>兩/施</span>所知則賵而不奠<span class='krp-note'>所知通問相知也降於/兄弟奠施於死者爲多</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3706:3734'><span class='krp-note'>故不/奠</span>知死者贈知生者賻<span class='krp-note'>各主於/所知</span>書賵於方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3734:3767'>若九若七若五<span class='krp-note'>方板也書賵奠賻贈之人名/與其物於板毎板若九行若</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3767:3801'><span class='krp-note'>七行若/五行</span>書遣於策<span class='krp-note'>策簡也遣猶送也謂/所當藏物茵以下</span>乃代</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3801:3832'>哭如初<span class='krp-note'>棺柩有時將去不忍絶/聲也𥘉謂旣小斂時</span>宵爲燎于門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3832:3860'>内之右<span class='krp-note'>爲哭者/爲明</span>厥明陳鼎五于門外如初<span class='krp-note'>鼎/五</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3860:3899'><span class='krp-note'>羊豕魚腊鮮獸各一鼎也士禮特牲三鼎盛/葬奠加一等用少牢也如𥘉如大歛奠時</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3899:3926'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-7b' );" name="013-7b" class="pb">[013-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3926:3959'>其實羊左胖<span class='krp-note'>反吉祭也言左胖/者體不殊骨也</span>髀不升<span class='krp-note'>周貴/肩賤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='3959:3991'><span class='krp-note'>髀古文/髀作脾</span>腸五胃五<span class='krp-note'>亦盛/之也</span>離肺<span class='krp-note'>離</span>豕亦如之豚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3991:4026'>解無腸胃<span class='krp-note'>如之如羊左胖髀不升離肺也豚/解解之如解豚亦前肩後肫春脅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4026:4061'><span class='krp-note'>而巳無腸胄者/君子不食溷腴</span>魚腊鮮獸皆如初<span class='krp-note'>鮮新殺者/士腊用兎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4061:4089'><span class='krp-note'>加鮮獸而無膚者/豕旣豚解略之</span>東方之饌四豆脾析蜱醢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4089:4121'>葵菹蠃醢<span class='krp-note'>脾讀爲雞脾肶之脾脾析百/葉也蜱蜯也今文蠃爲蝸</span>四籩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4121:4157'>棗糗栗脯<span class='krp-note'>糗以豆/糗粉餌</span>醴酒<span class='krp-note'>此東方之饌與祖奠/同在主人之南當前</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4157:4187'><span class='krp-note'>輅北上/巾之</span>陳器<span class='krp-note'>明噐也夜/敘藏之</span>滅燎執燭俠輅北靣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4187:4214'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-8a' );" name="013-8a" class="pb">[013-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4214:4247'><span class='krp-note'>炤徹與/葬奠也</span>賔入者拜之<span class='krp-note'>明自啓至此/主人無出禮</span>徹者入丈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4247:4277'>夫踊設于西北婦人踊<span class='krp-note'>猶阼階升時也亦旣/盥乃入入由重東而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4277:4315'><span class='krp-note'>主人踊猶其升也自重北西面而/徹設於柩車西北亦由序西南</span>徹者東<span class='krp-note'>由/柩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4315:4353'><span class='krp-note'>車北東適/葬奠之饌</span>鼎入<span class='krp-note'>舉入陳之也陳之蓋於/重東北西面北上如初</span>乃奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4353:4379'>豆南上綪籩蠃醢南北上綪<span class='krp-note'>籩蠃醢南/辟醴酒也</span>俎二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4379:4409'>以成南上不綪特鮮獸<span class='krp-note'>成猶併也不綪者魚/在羊東腊在豕東古</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4409:4438'><span class='krp-note'>文特/爲俎</span>醴酒在籩西北上<span class='krp-note'>統於/豆也</span>奠者出主人要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4438:4468'>節而踊<span class='krp-note'>亦以往來爲節奠由重/北西旣奠由重南東</span>甸人抗重出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4468:4495'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-8b' );" name="013-8b" class="pb">[013-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='4495:4528'>自道道左倚之<span class='krp-note'>還重不言甸人抗重言之者/重旣虞將埋之言其宫使守</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='4528:4567'><span class='krp-note'>視之抗舉也岀自道出從門中央也不由闑/東西者重不反變於恒出入道左主人位今</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='4567:4597'><span class='krp-note'>時有死者鑿木置食/其中樹於道側由此</span>薦馬馬出自道車各從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4597:4624'>其馬駕於門外西面而俟南上<span class='krp-note'>南上便其行/也行者乗車</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4624:4653'><span class='krp-note'>在前道/槀序從</span>徹者入踊如初徹巾苞牲取下體<span class='krp-note'>苞/者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4653:4692'><span class='krp-note'>象旣饗而歸賔俎者也取下體者脛骨象行/又俎實之終始也士苞三个前脛折取臂臑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4692:4730'><span class='krp-note'>後脛折取骼亦得俎釋三个雜/記曰父母而賔客之所以爲哀</span>不以魚腊<span class='krp-note'>非/正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4730:4766'><span class='krp-note'>牲/也</span>行器<span class='krp-note'>目葬行明器/在道之次</span>茵苞器序從<span class='krp-note'>如其陳/之先後</span>車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4766:4793'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-9a' );" name="013-9a" class="pb">[013-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4793:4824'>從<span class='krp-note'>次/噐</span>徹者出踊如初<span class='krp-note'>於是廟中當/行者唯柩車</span>主人之史</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='4824:4843'>請讀賵執筭從柩東當前束西面不命母哭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='4843:4866'>哭者相止也唯主人主婦哭燭在石南面<span class='krp-note'>史/北</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='4866:4904'><span class='krp-note'>面請旣而與執筭西面於主人之前讀書釋/筭燭在右南面炤書便也古文筭皆爲筴</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='4904:4929'>讀書釋筭則坐<span class='krp-note'>必釋筭者/榮其多</span>卒命哭滅燭書與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='4929:4952'>筭執之以逆出<span class='krp-note'>卒/巳</span>公史自西方東面命母哭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='4952:4976'>主人主婦皆不哭讀遣卒命哭滅燭出<span class='krp-note'>公史/君之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='4976:5012'><span class='krp-note'>典禮書者遣者入壙之物君使史來/讀之成其得禮之正以終也燭俠路</span>商祝執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5012:5039'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-9b' );" name="013-9b" class="pb">[013-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5039:5066'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-9b' );" name="013-9b" class="pb">[013-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5066:5104'>上<span class='krp-note'>統於/壙</span>茵先入<span class='krp-note'>當藉柩也元士則/葬用輁軸加茵焉</span>屬引<span class='krp-note'>於是/說載</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5104:5132'><span class='krp-note'>除飾更屬引於緘/耳古文屬爲燭</span>主人袒衆主人西面北上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5132:5156'>婦人東面皆不哭<span class='krp-note'>俠羡道/爲位</span>乃窆主人哭踊無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5156:5182'>筭<span class='krp-note'>窆下棺也今/文窆爲封</span>襲贈用制幣玄纁束拜稽顙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5182:5211'>踊如初<span class='krp-note'>丈八尺曰制二制/合之束十制五合</span>卒袒拜賔主婦亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5211:5239'>拜賔即位拾踊三襲<span class='krp-note'>主婦拜賔拜女/賔也卽位反位</span>賔出則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5239:5270'>拜送<span class='krp-note'>相問之賔也凡弔賔有/五去皆拜之此舉中焉</span>藏器於旁加見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5270:5309'><span class='krp-note'>噐用器役器也見棺飾也更謂之見者加此/則棺柩不復見矣先言藏噐乃云加見者噐</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5309:5337'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-10a' );" name="013-10a" class="pb">[013-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5337:5376'><span class='krp-note'>在見内也内之者明君子之於事終不自逸/也檀弓曰有虞氏之瓦棺夏后氏堲周殷人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5376:5412'><span class='krp-note'>棺椁周人/牆置翣</span>藏苞筲於旁<span class='krp-note'>於旁者在見外也不/言罋甒饌相次可知</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5412:5446'><span class='krp-note'>四者兩兩而居䘮大託曰棺椁/之間君容祝大夫容壺士容甒</span>加折卻之加</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5446:5469'>抗席覆之加抗木<span class='krp-note'>冝次/也</span>實土三主人拜鄕人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5469:5498'><span class='krp-note'>謝其/勤勞</span>即位踊襲如初<span class='krp-note'>哀親之/在斯</span>乃反哭入升自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5498:5524'>西階東面衆主人堂下東面北上<span class='krp-note'>西階東面/反諸其所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5524:5555'><span class='krp-note'>作也反哭者於其祖庿不/於阼階西面西方神位</span>婦人入大夫踊升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='5555:5579'>自阼階<span class='krp-note'>辟主/人也</span>主婦入于室踊出即位及丈夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='5579:5607'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-10b' );" name="013-10b" class="pb">[013-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='5607:5639'>拾踊三<span class='krp-note'>入于室反諸其所養也出/卽位堂上西面也拾更也</span>賔弔者升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='5639:5666'>自西階曰如之何主人拜稽顙<span class='krp-note'>賔弔者衆賔/之長也反而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='5666:5705'><span class='krp-note'>亡焉失之矣於是爲甚故弔之弔者北面主/人拜於位不北面拜賔東者以其亦主人位</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='5705:5729'><span class='krp-note'>也今文/無曰</span>賔降出主人送于門外拜稽顙遂適</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='5729:5758'>殯宮皆如啓位拾踊三<span class='krp-note'>啓位婦人入升堂/丈夫即中庭之位</span>兄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='5758:5787'>弟出主人拜送<span class='krp-note'>兄弟小功以下也異/門大功亦可以歸</span>衆主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='5787:5811'>出門哭止闔門主人揖衆主人乃就次<span class='krp-note'>次倚/廬也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='5811:5844'>猶朝夕哭不奠<span class='krp-note'>是日也以/虞易奠</span>三虞<span class='krp-note'>虞䘮祭名虞/安也骨肉歸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='5844:5872'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-11a' );" name="013-11a" class="pb">[013-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='5872:5909'><span class='krp-note'>於土精氣無所不之孝子爲其彷徨三/祭以安之朝葬日中而虞不忍一日離</span>卒哭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='5909:5944'><span class='krp-note'>卒哭三虞之後祭名始朝夕之間哀/至則哭至此祭止也朝夕哭而巳</span>明日以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='5944:5980'>其班祔<span class='krp-note'>班次也袝卒哭之明日祭名祔猶屬/也祭昭穆之次而屬之今文班爲胖</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='5980:6007'>記士處適寢寢東首于北墉下<span class='krp-note'>將有疾乃寢/於適室今文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6007:6041'><span class='krp-note'>處爲居/于爲於</span>有疾疾者齊<span class='krp-note'>正情性也適寢者/不齊不居其室</span>養者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6041:6075'>皆齊<span class='krp-note'>憂/也</span>徹琴瑟<span class='krp-note'>去/樂</span>疾病外内皆埽<span class='krp-note'>爲有賔客/來問也疾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6075:6106'><span class='krp-note'>甚曰/病</span>徹褺衣加新衣<span class='krp-note'>故衣垢汗爲/來人穢惡之</span>御者四人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='6106:6135'>皆坐持體<span class='krp-note'>爲不能自轉側御/者今時侍從之人</span>屬纊以俟絶氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='6135:6163'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-11b' );" name="013-11b" class="pb">[013-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='6163:6190'><span class='krp-note'>爲其氣微難/節也纊新絮</span>男子不絶於婦人之手婦人不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='6190:6220'>絶於男子之手<span class='krp-note'>備/褻</span>乃行禱于五祀<span class='krp-note'>盡孝子之/情五祀博</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='6220:6255'><span class='krp-note'>言之士二祀/曰門曰行</span>乃卒<span class='krp-note'>卒終/也</span>主人啼兄弟哭<span class='krp-note'>哀有/甚有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='6255:6288'><span class='krp-note'>否於是始去笄纚服深衣檀/弓曰始死羔裘玄冠者易之</span>設牀第當牖衽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='6288:6320'>下筦上簟設枕<span class='krp-note'>病卒之間廢牀至是設之事/相變祍卧席古文第爲茨</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='6320:6347'>遷尸<span class='krp-note'>徙於牖下也於/是幠用歛衾</span>復者朝服左執領右執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='6347:6378'>要招而左<span class='krp-note'>衣朝服服/未可以變</span>楔貌如軛上兩末<span class='krp-note'>事便/也今</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='6378:6407'><span class='krp-note'>文軛/作厄</span>綴足用燕几校在南御者坐持之<span class='krp-note'>校脛/也尸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='6407:6435'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-12a' );" name="013-12a" class="pb">[013-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='6435:6467'><span class='krp-note'>南首几脛在南以拘足則/不得辟戾矣古文校爲枝</span>即牀而奠當腢用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='6467:6497'>吉噐若醴若酒無巾柶<span class='krp-note'>腢肩頭也用吉器器/未變也或卒無醴用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='6497:6520'><span class='krp-note'>新/酒</span>赴曰君之臣某死赴母妻長子則曰君之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='6520:6546'>臣某之某死<span class='krp-note'>赴走告也今/文赴作訃</span>室中唯主人主婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='6546:6570'>坐兄弟有命夫命婦在焉亦坐<span class='krp-note'>别尊/卑也</span>尸在室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='6570:6593'>有君命衆主人不出<span class='krp-note'>不二/主</span>襚者委衣于牀不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='6593:6622'>坐<span class='krp-note'>牀高/由便</span>其禭于室戸西北面致命<span class='krp-note'>始死/時也</span>夏祝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='6622:6645'>淅米差盛之<span class='krp-note'>差擇/之</span>御者四人抗衾而浴䄠第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='6645:6673'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-12b' );" name="013-12b" class="pb">[013-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='6673:6704'><span class='krp-note'>抗衾爲其倮程蔽之也䄠/袒也袒簀去席盝水便</span>其母之䘮則内御</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='6704:6733'>者浴鬠無笄<span class='krp-note'>内御女御也無笄/猶丈夫之不冠也</span>設明衣婦人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='6733:6758'>則設中帶<span class='krp-note'>中帶若今/之禪襂</span>卒洗貝反于䈂實貝柱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='6758:6789'>右齻左齻<span class='krp-note'>象齒/堅</span>夏祝徹餘飯<span class='krp-note'>徹去/鬻</span>瑱塞耳<span class='krp-note'>塞/充</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='6789:6814'><span class='krp-note'>窒</span>掘坎南順廣尺輪二尺深三尺南其壤<span class='krp-note'>南/順</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='6814:6848'><span class='krp-note'>統於堂輪從也/今文掘爲坅</span>垼用塊<span class='krp-note'>塊堛也古/文垼爲役</span>明衣裳用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='6848:6879'>幕布袂屬幅長下膝<span class='krp-note'>幕布帷幕之布升數未/聞也屬幅不削幅也長</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='6879:6911'><span class='krp-note'>下膝又有裳於/蔽下體深也</span>有前後裳不辟長及觳<span class='krp-note'>不辟/質也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='6911:6939'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-13a' );" name="013-13a" class="pb">[013-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='6939:6978'><span class='krp-note'>觳足跗也凡他服短/無見膚長無𬒳土</span>縓綼緆<span class='krp-note'>一染謂之縓今/紅也飾裳在幅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='6978:7019'><span class='krp-note'>曰綼在/下曰緆</span>緇純<span class='krp-note'>七入爲緇緇黒也飾衣曰純謂/領與𬒮衣以緇裳以縓象天地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='7019:7047'><span class='krp-note'>也</span>設握裏親膚繫鉤中指結于掔<span class='krp-note'>掔掌後節/中也手無</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='7047:7083'><span class='krp-note'>決者以握繫一端繞掔還從/上自貫反與其一端結之</span>甸人築坅坎<span class='krp-note'>築/實</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='7083:7121'><span class='krp-note'>土其中堅之穿/坎之名一曰坅</span>隷人涅廁<span class='krp-note'>隷人罪人也今之/徒役作者也涅塞</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='7121:7153'><span class='krp-note'>也爲人復往褻之/又亦鬼神不用</span>旣襲宵爲燎于中庭<span class='krp-note'>宵/夜</span>厥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='7153:7181'>明滅燎陳衣<span class='krp-note'>記/節</span>凡絞紟用布倫如朝服<span class='krp-note'>凡凡/小斂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='7181:7210'><span class='krp-note'>大斂也倫比也今文/無紟古文倫爲輪</span>設棜于東堂下南順齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='7210:7238'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-13b' );" name="013-13b" class="pb">[013-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='7238:7257'>于坫饌于其上兩甒醴酒酒在南篚在東南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='7257:7276'>順實角觶四木柶二素勺二豆在甒北二以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='7276:7310'>並籩亦如之<span class='krp-note'>棜今之轝也角觶四木柶二素/勺爲少進醴酒兼饌之也勺二</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='7310:7349'><span class='krp-note'>醴酒各一也豆籩二以併則是大歛饌也記/於此者明其他與小歛同陳古文角觶爲角</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='7349:7380'><span class='krp-note'>柶</span>凡籩豆實具設皆巾之<span class='krp-note'>籩豆偶而爲具具/則於饌巾之巾之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='7380:7408'><span class='krp-note'>加飾也明小斂/一豆一籩不巾</span>觶俟時而酌柶覆加之面枋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='7408:7437'>及錯建之<span class='krp-note'>時朝夕也檀弓曰朝/奠日出夕奠逮日</span>小斂辟奠不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='7437:7473'>出室<span class='krp-note'>未忍神逺之也辟襲奠以辟斂旣斂則/不出於室設於序西南畢事而去之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='7473:7501'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-14a' );" name="013-14a" class="pb">[013-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='7501:7526'>無踊節<span class='krp-note'>其哀未/可節也</span>旣馮尸主人袒髺髮絞帶衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='7526:7559'>主人布帶<span class='krp-note'>衆主人齊/衰以下</span>大斂于阼<span class='krp-note'>未忍便離主/人位也主人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='7559:7586'><span class='krp-note'>奉尸斂于棺則/西階上賔之</span>大夫升自西階階東北面東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='7586:7614'>上<span class='krp-note'>視/斂</span>旣馮尸大夫逆降復位<span class='krp-note'>中庭西/面位</span>巾奠執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='7614:7638'>燭者滅燭出降自阼階由主人之北東<span class='krp-note'>巾奠/而室</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='7638:7674'><span class='krp-note'>事/巳</span>旣殯主人說髦<span class='krp-note'>旣殯置銘于肂復位時也/今文說皆作稅兒生三月</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='7674:7713'><span class='krp-note'>鬋髪爲鬌男角女羈否則男左女右長大猶/爲飾存之謂之髦所以順父母幼小之心至</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='7713:7751'><span class='krp-note'>此尸柩不見䘮無飾可/以去之髦之形象未聞</span>三日絞垂<span class='krp-note'>成服日絞/要絰之散</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='7751:7779'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-14b' );" name="013-14b" class="pb">[013-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='7779:7812'><span class='krp-note'>垂/者</span>冠六升外縪纓條屬厭<span class='krp-note'>縪謂縫著於武也/外者外其餘也纓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='7812:7849'><span class='krp-note'>條屬者通屈一條繩爲武/垂下爲纓屬之冠厭伏也</span>衰三升<span class='krp-note'>衣與/裳也</span>屨外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='7849:7883'>納<span class='krp-note'>納收/餘也</span>杖下本竹桐一也<span class='krp-note'>順其/性也</span>居倚廬<span class='krp-note'>倚木/爲廬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='7883:7920'><span class='krp-note'>在中門外/東方北戶</span>寢苫枕塊<span class='krp-note'>苫編藁/塊堛也</span>不說絰帶<span class='krp-note'>哀戚/不在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='7920:7955'><span class='krp-note'>於/安</span>哭晝夜無時<span class='krp-note'>哀至則哭/非必朝夕</span>非䘮事不言<span class='krp-note'>不忘/所以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='7955:7983'><span class='krp-note'>爲/親</span>歠粥朝一溢米夕一溢米不食菜果<span class='krp-note'>不在/於飽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='7983:8020'><span class='krp-note'>與滋味粥糜也二十兩曰溢爲米一升二/十四分升之一實在木曰果在地曰蓏</span>主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='8020:8055'>人乗惡車<span class='krp-note'>拜君命拜衆賔及有故行所乗也/雜記曰端衰䘮車皆無等然則此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='8055:8083'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-15a' );" name="013-15a" class="pb">[013-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='8083:8121'><span class='krp-note'>惡車王䘮之木車/也古文惡作堊</span>白狗幦<span class='krp-note'>未成豪狗幦覆笭/也以狗皮爲之取</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='8121:8159'><span class='krp-note'>其臑也白於䘮飾/宜古文幦爲幂</span>蒲蔽<span class='krp-note'>蔽/藩</span>御以蒲菆<span class='krp-note'>不在於/驅馳蒲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='8159:8197'><span class='krp-note'>菆牡蒲莖古/文菆作騶</span>犬服<span class='krp-note'>笭間兵服以犬皮爲之取/堅也亦白今文犬爲大</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='8197:8234'>木錧<span class='krp-note'>取少聲今/文錧爲鎋</span>約綏約轡<span class='krp-note'>約繩綏所/以引升車</span>木鑣<span class='krp-note'>亦/取</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='8234:8271'><span class='krp-note'>少聲古文/鑣爲苞</span>馬不齊髦<span class='krp-note'>齊翦也今文髦爲毛主/人之惡車如王之木車</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='8271:8301'><span class='krp-note'>則齊衰以下其乗素/車繅車駹車漆車與</span>主婦之車亦如之䟽布</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='8301:8336'>裧<span class='krp-note'>裧者車裳幃/於蓋弓垂之</span>貳車白狗攝服<span class='krp-note'>貳副也攝猶/縁也狗皮緣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='8336:8364'><span class='krp-note'>服差/飾</span>其他皆如乗車<span class='krp-note'>如所乗/惡車</span>朔月童子執帚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='8364:8392'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-15b' );" name="013-15b" class="pb">[013-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='8392:8424'>卻之左手奉之<span class='krp-note'>童子隷子弟若内竪寺人之/屬執用左手卻之示未用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='8424:8449'>從徹者而入<span class='krp-note'>童子不/專禮事</span>比奠舉席埽室聚諸㝔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='8449:8468'>布席如初卒奠埽者執帚垂末内鬛從執燭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='8468:8495'>者而東<span class='krp-note'>比猶先也室東/南隅謂之㝔</span>燕養饋羞湯沐之饌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='8495:8531'>如他日<span class='krp-note'>燕養平常所用供養也饋朝夕食也/羞四時之珍異湯沐所以洗去汙垢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='8531:8570'><span class='krp-note'>内則曰三日具沐五日具浴孝子不忍一日/廢其事親之禮於下室日設之如生存也進</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='8570:8601'><span class='krp-note'>徹之時/如其頃</span>朔月若薦新則不饋于下室<span class='krp-note'>以其殷/奠有黍</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='8601:8637'><span class='krp-note'>稷也下室如今之/内堂正寢聽朝事</span>筮宅冡人物土<span class='krp-note'>物猶相也/相其地可</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='8637:8665'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-16a' );" name="013-16a" class="pb">[013-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='8665:8689'><span class='krp-note'>葬者乃/營之</span>卜曰吉告從于主婦主婦哭婦人皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='8689:8712'>哭主婦升堂哭者皆止<span class='krp-note'>事/畢</span>啓之昕外内不哭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='8712:8742'><span class='krp-note'>將有事爲其讙嚻旣/啓命哭古文啓爲開</span>夷牀輁軸饌于西階東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='8742:8781'><span class='krp-note'>明階間者位近西也夷牀饌於祖庿輁軸饌/於殯宫其二庿者於禰亦饌輁軸焉古文輁</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='8781:8808'><span class='krp-note'>或作/拱</span>其二庿則饌于禰庿如小斂奠乃啓<span class='krp-note'>祖/尊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='8808:8837'><span class='krp-note'>禰卑也士事祖禰上/士異庿下士共庿</span>朝于禰庿重止于門外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='8837:8856'>之西東面柩入升自西階正柩于兩楹間奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='8856:8875'>止于西階之下東面北上主人升柩東西面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='8875:8903'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-16b' );" name="013-16b" class="pb">[013-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='8903:8922'>衆主人東即位婦人從升東面奠升設于柩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='8922:8949'>西升降自西階主人要節而踊<span class='krp-note'>重不入者主/於朝祖而行</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='8949:8977'><span class='krp-note'>若過之矣門西/東面待之便也</span>燭先入者升堂東楹之南西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='8977:9005'>面後入者西階東北面在下<span class='krp-note'>炤正柩者先先/柩者後後柩者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='9005:9032'><span class='krp-note'>適祖時燭亦/然互記於此</span>主人降即位徹乃奠升降自西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='9032:9063'>階主人踊如初<span class='krp-note'>如其降拜賔至於要節/而踊不薦車不從此行</span>祝及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='9063:9082'>執事舉奠巾席從而降柩從序從如初適祖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='9082:9121'><span class='krp-note'>此謂朝禰明日舉奠適祖之序也此祝執醴/先酒脯醢俎從之巾席爲後旣正柩席升設</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='9121:9149'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-17a' );" name="013-17a" class="pb">[013-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='9149:9189'><span class='krp-note'>設奠如𥘉祝受巾巾之凡䘮自卒至殯自啓/至葬主人之禮其變同則此日數亦同矣序</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='9189:9215'><span class='krp-note'>從主人以下/今文無從</span>薦乗車鹿淺幦干笮革靾載旜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='9215:9243'>載皮弁服纓轡貝勒縣于衡<span class='krp-note'>士乗棧車鹿淺/鹿夏毛也幦覆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='9243:9289'><span class='krp-note'>笭玉藻曰士齊車鹿幦豹犆干盾也笮矢箙/也靾韁也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0950' title='KR0950' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0950.png'/>旌旗之屬通帛爲旜孤卿之所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='9289:9328'><span class='krp-note'>建亦攝焉皮弁服者視朔之服貝勒貝飾勒/有于無兵有箙無弓矢明不用古文靾爲殺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='9328:9364'><span class='krp-note'>旜爲/膳</span>道車載朝服<span class='krp-note'>道車朝夕及燕出入之車/朝服日視朝服之也玄衣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='9364:9401'><span class='krp-note'>素/裳</span>稾車載蓑笠<span class='krp-note'>稾猶散也散車以田以鄙之/車蓑笠備雨服今文稾爲潦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='9401:9430'><span class='krp-note'>凡道車稾車之纓轡/及勒亦縣于衡也</span>將載祝及執事舉奠戶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='9430:9458'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-17b' );" name="013-17b" class="pb">[013-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='9458:9486'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-17b' );" name="013-17b" class="pb">[013-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='9486:9513'>至道左北面立東上<span class='krp-note'>道左墓道東/先至者在東</span>柩至于壙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='9513:9548'>斂服載之<span class='krp-note'>柩車至壙祝說載除飾乃歛乗車/道車槀車之服載之不空之以歸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='9548:9584'><span class='krp-note'>送形而往迎精/而反亦禮之冝</span>卒窆而歸不驅<span class='krp-note'>孝子往如慕/反如疑爲親</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='9584:9607'><span class='krp-note'>之在/彼</span>君視斂若不待奠加蓋而出不視斂則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='9607:9633'>加蓋而至卒事<span class='krp-note'>爲有他故/及辟忌也</span>旣正柩賔出遂匠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='9633:9667'>納車于階間<span class='krp-note'>遂匠遂人匠人也遂人主引徒/役匠人主載柩窆職相左右也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='9667:9706'><span class='krp-note'>車載柩車周禮謂之蜃車雜記謂之團或作/輇或作摶聲讀皆相附耳未聞孰正其車之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='9706:9745'><span class='krp-note'>轝狀如牀中央有轅前後出設前後輅轝上/有四周下則前後有軸以輇爲輪許叔重說</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='9745:9773'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-18a' );" name="013-18a" class="pb">[013-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='9773:9799'><span class='krp-note'>有輻曰輪/無輻曰輇</span>祝饌祖奠于主人之南當前輅北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='9799:9829'>上巾之<span class='krp-note'>言饌於主人之南當/前輅則旣祖祝乃饌</span>弓矢之新沽功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='9829:9866'><span class='krp-note'>設之冝新沽示不/用今文沽作古</span>有弭飾焉<span class='krp-note'>弓無縁者謂之/弭弭以骨角爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='9866:9903'><span class='krp-note'>飾</span>亦張可也<span class='krp-note'>亦使/可張</span>有柲<span class='krp-note'>柲弓檠弛則縳之於/弓裏備損傷以竹爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='9903:9941'><span class='krp-note'>之詩云竹柲緄/縢今文柲作枈</span>設依撻焉<span class='krp-note'>依纒絃也撻弣側/矢道也皆以韋爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='9941:9973'><span class='krp-note'>之今文/撻爲銛</span>有韣<span class='krp-note'>韣弓衣也以/緇布爲之</span>翭矢一乗骨鏃短</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='9973:10011'>衞<span class='krp-note'>翭猶候也候物而射之矢也四矢曰乗骨/鏃短衛亦示不用也生時翭矢金鏃凡爲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='10011:10042'><span class='krp-note'>矢五分笴長/而羽其一</span>志矢一乗軒輖中亦短衞<span class='krp-note'>志猶/擬也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='10042:10070'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-18b' );" name="013-18b" class="pb">[013-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='10070:10109'><span class='krp-note'>習射之矢書云若射之有志輖摯也無鏃短/衛亦示不用生時志矢骨鏃凡爲矢前重後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='10109:10116'><span class='krp-note'>輕/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='10116:10124'>儀禮卷第十三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='10124:10148'><span class='krp-note'>經二千五百一/注五千四十七</span>十<span class='krp-note'>六字/字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='10148:10176'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-19a' );" name="013-19a" class="pb">[013-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='10176:10204'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0026', 'SBCK', '013-20a' );" name="013-20a" class="pb">[013-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
